# {{ project_name | pascal }} - AMQP 1.0 Consumer

Auto-generated Go AMQP 1.0 consumer using `github.com/Azure/go-amqp` with CloudEvents structured and binary content modes.

## Quick start

```go
consumer, err := {{ project_name | snake }}.New{{ class_name }}("amqp://localhost:5672", "events", handler)
if err != nil {
    log.Fatal(err)
}
defer consumer.Close(context.Background())

if err := consumer.Start(context.Background()); err != nil {
    log.Fatal(err)
}
```

Use `New{{ class_name }}WithReceiver` to inject a test receiver without a broker.
